@gillianoberholzer @shaunviljoen @jakovanrensburg 

Hi - TU took the request in question off their server, so I don't have any access to it anymore.

I've went through a few requests on the server(downloaded PDF's, served to clients) and they all have bank codes.

TU also admitted that this request did not contain a bank code.

Really don't think there is any more we can do here.

Just a note: I suspect TU removes the request from their server after a week or so, as this response came in on 29 June.
